190
00:12:23,909 --> 00:12:24,919
Hey!

191
00:12:25,649 --> 00:12:27,750
Hey! You punk!

192
00:12:36,190 --> 00:12:37,259
Hey!

193
00:12:48,009 --> 00:12:49,639
Hey, you!

194
00:14:16,690 --> 00:14:17,700
