199
00:14:28,240 --> 00:14:30,768
I'm Kim Deuk Pal, the number
two man in the Chilsung Gang.

200
00:14:30,769 --> 00:14:31,840
There's no way I...

201
00:14:40,519 --> 00:14:42,359
