229
00:16:28,659 --> 00:16:29,730
This isn't a dream.

230
00:16:32,799 --> 00:16:34,869
What? What happened?

231
00:16:34,870 --> 00:16:36,200
You punk!

232
00:16:37,429 --> 00:16:40,739
